    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork is cooking, pierce your<strong> red potato[es]</strong> with a fork, then add to a plate and cook in the <strong>microwave</strong> for 10-12 min or until cooked through</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
