    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, trim, then slice your <strong>spring onion[s]</strong></p><p>Grate your <strong>cheddar cheese</strong></p><p>Add your <strong>shredded red cabbage </strong>to a large bowl with <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soured cream </strong>(you'll use the rest later!), your <strong>cider vinegar</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>sugar </strong>and mix it all together – this is your <strong>cabbage slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
