      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 30 min, remove the pulled pork dish from the oven and discard the <strong>tin foil</strong></p><p>Pull the <strong>BBQ pulled</strong> <strong>pork</strong> apart using two forks, then add<strong> </strong>your <strong>honey</strong> and give everything a good mix up</p><p>Return the dish to the oven for a final 5-6 min or until the sauce has reduced and the pork has started to crisp – this is your <strong>smoky Cajun-style pulled pork</strong></p>",
