    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the pork is in the oven, slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Add the <strong>brioche halves</strong> to a baking tray, cut side up, and put the tray in the oven for 4-5 min or until warmed through</p>",
