    {
      "instruction": "<p>To build your burger, top each <strong>toasted brioche base</strong> with the <strong>smoky Cajun-style pulled pork</strong>, a handful of <strong>cabbage slaw </strong>and a <strong>toasted brioche lid</strong> – this is your <strong>Cajun-style pulled pork burger</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> Cajun-style pulled pork burger </strong>with the<strong> cheesy potato skins</strong> and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>cabbage slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
